<h1>About the Oxford University Scientific Society</h1>

<h2 id="com">The current committee</h2>

<p>The activity required to maintain the smooth running of
the society is provided by the Committee, a group of selfless,
CV-obsessed individuals devoted to running the society,
ensuring that the speakers turn up and are fed, ensuring that
more speakers turn up for next term, ensuring that the audience
turns up, putting up pretty posters, and sending out emails
to alert everyone of what the Society will do next.</p>

