<h2>Join the committee</h2>

<p>
There is a high turnover of committee members, so we are constantly seeking
committed, resourceful people to join the team of students who are responsible
for the running of one of Oxford's oldest and largest societies. There are a
variety of posts available catering for different skills and interests.  If
there are none you like, we can invent one for you.  Everyone is welcome at
committee meetings.  Elections for next term will take place after the last
lecture of each term (this year in Week 8, Wednesday 6th March 2013).
</p>

